import { Button, FormControl, Input, Stack } from "@chakra-ui/react";

export function LoginForm() {
  return (
    <>
    <FormControl>
      <Input placeholder="email" />
      <Input 
        placeholder="password" 
        type="password" 
      />
        <Button 
          width='full' 
          mt={4} 
          colorScheme='blue' 
          size="md">
            Acessar
        </Button>
        </FormControl>
    </>
  )
}
